Quote: Left England in command of the Harpooner, South Sea Whaler, on the 12th of April, 1842, left the ship in Hobart Town, 1847, afterwards went to Adelaide, from thence to some part of New Zealand, and is supposed to be either in Her Majesty's Customs or in a pilot brig at Auckland or Wellington.
